elephone code\n| area_code               = 91-079\n| registration_plate      =GJ \n| blank1_name_sec1        = [[Lok Sabha]] constituency\n| blank1_info_sec1        = [[Ahmedabad West]]\n| blank2_name_sec1        = [[Vidhan Sabha]] constituency\n| blank2_info_sec1        = Ellisbridge\n| blank3_name_sec1        = Civic agency\n| blank3_info_sec1        = [[Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation]]\n| website                 = {{URL|gujaratindia.com}} \n| footnotes               = \n}}\n'''Paldi''' is an affluent area located in South Western [[Ahmedabad]], [[India]].<ref>[http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_ahmedabads-posh-areas-soft-targets-for-criminals_1264175 Ahmedabad\u2019s posh areas soft targets for criminals]</ref> Corporate offices and city centres of many national and international companies like [[ICICI Bank]], [[Royal Bank of Scotland]], [[Religare]], [[ Claris]], [[Gujarat Gas]] are located within Paldi. It accommodates [[Sanskar Kendra]] museum by the renowned architect [[Le Corbusier]] as well as [[Tagore Memorial Hall]]. The [[National Institute of Design]] is located in Paldi.<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-10-25/ahmedabad/28240997_1_nid-design-museum NID to set up first ever design museum]</ref>\n\n==Religious places==\n* Bawa Tawakkal Dargah\n* Dharnidhar Jain Derasar\n* Jalaram Mandir\n* Mahalaxmi Temple\n* Sai Baba Temple\n* Shahi Masjid\n\n==Education==\n* Amrit Jyoti High School\n* Ankur School\n* Diwan Ballubhai School\n* Little Flower School\n* Mahavir Vidyalaya\n* [[National Institute of Design]]\n* Navchetan High School\n* P T College\n* Pulkit School\n* Sadhana School\n* Sharda Mandir School\n* Shri Rambali Vidhayamandir\n* Smt NHL Medical College\n* Trinity English School\n* V R Shah School\n* Vandana Vidhya Vihar\n\n==Hospitals==\n* AIMS Hospital\n* Aneri Eye Hospital\n* ESI Dispensary\n* Indian Red Cross Society, Ahmedabad\n* Long Life Hospital\n* Sanjivani Hospital\n* Shubham Maternity Hospital                                           * Shaurya Hospital\n\n==Transportation==\n* [[Ahmedabad Railway Station]] is approximately 7&nbsp;km from Paldi.\n* [[Gujarat State Road Transport Corporation]] Bus Station, Gita Mandir is approximately 2&nbsp;km from Paldi.\n* [[Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel International Airport]] is approximately 16&nbsp;km from Paldi.\n\n==Hotels==\t\n* [http://www.legranderesidency.in/ Le Grande]\t\n* [http://www.platinumhotels.in/ Hotel Platinum Inn]\t\n* [http://www.hotelthewestend.com/ The Westend, Ahmedabad]\n* [http://www.hotelriverfront.co.in/ Hotel Riverfront, Ahmedabad]\n* Hotel Heritage\t\n* Hotel Skylon\n\n==Restaurants/Cafes==\t\n* [http://havmor.com Havmor]\n* [http://www.honestrestaurant.com Honest]\n* [http://www.subway.co.in Subway] (One and only pure veg. outlet in the world, also serving jain<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-03-06/ahmedabad/37498833_1_vegetarian-cuisine-vegetarian-food-durlabh-singh World's first pure veg. Subway outlet opens in Paldi]</ref>\t\n* [http://www.cafecoffeeday.com Cafe Coffee Day]\n* Udipi Cafe\n* [http://www.uspizza.in U S Pizza]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Ahmedabad topics}}\n\n[[Category:Neighbourhoods in Ahmedabad]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=June 2018}}\n{{rewrite|date=March 2017}}\n{{for|the settlement in Canada|Paldi, British Columbia}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Paldi\n| other_name              = \n| nickname                = \n| settlement_type         = Neighbourhood\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| pushpin_map             = India Gujarat#India\n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in Gujarat, India\n| coordinates             = {{coord|23|0|22|N|72|33|53|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1       = [